  m_Name: Princes And Favourites
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FlightPaper.ProjectSorrow.Poems.PoemScriptableObject
  id: 62
  title: Princes And Favourites
  author: Robert Herrick
  isFemaleAuthor: 0
  stanzas:
  - lines:
    - Princes and fav'rites are most dear, while they
    - By giving and receiving hold the play;
    - But the relation then of both grows poor,
    - When these can ask, and kings can give no more.
  rating: 0
